      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and cook for 1 min or until the Chinese rice wine has evaporated</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken stock </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling reduce to medium and cook for an initial 10 min or until the potatoes are fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
