          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain your <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>After an initial 10 min, add the <strong>drained sweetcorn </strong>and <strong>spinach </strong>to the pan for a final 5 min or until the spinach has wilted and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
