    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, stir through your <strong>soft cheese </strong>with<strong> </strong>a good grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy chicken thigh & sweetcorn chowder</strong></p><p>Discard the thyme stalks<strong> </strong>and shred any larger pieces of chicken apart, using two forks</p>",
