    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy chicken thigh & sweetcorn chowder </strong>in bowls</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining smoked paprika</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of<strong> pepper </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
